**SOLO MINING GUIDE**
```
1. Download this:
https://github.com/Seal-Clubber/ravencoin-stratum-proxy/tree/mewc

2. MAKE SURE you extract it to a folder called "ravencoin-stratum-proxy"

3. Run the windows/generate_bat.bat file and follow instructions (I used port 8767).

4. Add the following to your meowcoin.conf:
  rpcuser=username
  rpcpassword=password
  rpcallowip=127.0.0.1
  rpcport=8766
  miningaddress=YOUR_WALLET_ADDRESS
  server=1

5. Run MEWC wallet.

6. Run the new run.bat file that was generated in the stratum folder.

7. Run your miner (I use t-rex):
t-rex.exe -a kawpow -o 127.0.0.1:8767 --user YOU_WALLET_ADDRESS -p password

(will in YOUR_WALLET_ADDRESS with your wallet address... Obviously)
```

If you are having PEER issues, you can fix this quickly connecting to my Meowcoin Node. Follow the below steps.

1. Open up your console in Core wallet. "Tools" -> "Information" -> Console tab 
2. Type "addnode 122.58.153.242:8788 add" (remove "") and press enter.
3. It will return a "null" response - ignore this. 
4. Done! Now wait for download to complete.

Alternatively, you can add the node to your meowcoin.conf file. You can open this by:
1. Wallet Tab -> Options in core wallet 
2. In the options menu, make sure you have selected the "Main" tab.
3. Click open configuration file

type "addnode=122.58.153.242:8788" into this file and click save. 

4. You will need to **restart** your wallet for it to recognize the changes in the meowcoin.conf file.
5. Done! Now wait for download to complete.
